  "markdown": "[Skip to content](https://popsindustrial.com/request-a-quote/facilities-equipment/#content)\n\n# Facilities & Equipment\n\n[![](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Pops-arial-photo-2-300x199.jpg)](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Pops-arial-photo-2.jpg)\n\n[![](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Industrial-Powder-Coating-Service-Lakeland-FL-scaled-1-225x300.jpg)](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Industrial-Powder-Coating-Service-Lakeland-FL-scaled-1.jpg)\n\n[![](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/pops-industrial-coatings-lakeland-fl-facility-01-1-300x225.jpg)](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/pops-industrial-coatings-lakeland-fl-facility-01-1.jpg)\n\n[![](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/pops-industrial-coatings-lakeland-fl-facility-02-1-300x225.jpg)](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/pops-industrial-coatings-lakeland-fl-facility-02-1.jpg)\n\n![](https://popsindustrial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/large-capacity-powder-coating-270x138-1.png)\n\n## Our  **Services**\n\nWe pride ourselves in our extensive services and quality products, offering customers one-stop shopping from small to large projects.\n\n[Learn More](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/)\n\n## Our  **Certifications**\n\nWe adhere to strict industry specifications and best practices to achieve the utmost in quality workmanship. See our certifications.\n\n[Learn More](https://popsindustrial.com/request-a-quote/standards-specifications-certifications/)\n\n## What makes us  **Different**\n\nPop’s offers experience and expertise. Read about makes us different, solidifying our position as a leader in industrial coatings.\n\n[Learn More](https://popsindustrial.com/about-us/)",
